# Visual-diff generated image artifacts — large (~530M) and fully regenerable via
# scripts/visual-diff (capture.ts clone + diff.ts). The Phase 0 ORIGINAL baseline
# PNGs are committed; clone shots, raw HTML snapshots, and diff-report images are
# NOT (regenerate locally). See docs/reference/NEXT_STEPS.md for git-lfs guidance.
